50 typedef struct _OpcUa_ReferenceNode
51 {
52  SOPC_EncodeableType* encodeableType;
53  /* IMPORTANT NOTE: response header IN RESPONSE MSG BODY is kept only
54  * for giving a copy of the header to application.
55  */
56  SOPC_NodeId ReferenceTypeId;
57  SOPC_Boolean IsInverse;
58  SOPC_ExpandedNodeId TargetId;
59 } OpcUa_ReferenceNode;
60

69 #endif
